text: Josef Šváb (born 8 June 1933) is a Czech former sports shooter. He competed in the 25 metre pistol event at the 1960 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1933 births Category:Living people Category:Czech male sport shooters Category:Olympic shooters of Czechoslovakia Category:Shooters at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Plzeň
